          <title>
            <string language="en">Types of bonds in protein</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Typen der Bindungen im Protein</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Types d'obligations en protéine</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Tipos de ligações na proteína</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Tipi di legami in proteina</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Τύποι δεσμών στην πρωτεϊ'νη</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Tipos de enlaces en proteína</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">This illustration shows the different kinds of bonds found in protein structures. These are: (a) hydrogen bonds, (b) disulphide bonds, (c) ionic bonds and (d) hydrophobic interactions.</string>
          </description>
          <language>x-none</language>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">hydrogen bonds</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">hydrophobic interactions</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">ionic bonds</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>

          </keyword>
          <structure>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Diese Abbildung zeigt die unterschiedlichen Arten 
der Bindungen, die in den Proteinstrukturen gefunden werden. 
Diese sind: (a) bindet Wasserstoff, (b) Disulfidbindungen,
(c) Ionenbindungen und (d) hydrophobe Interaktionen ab.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Cette illustration montre les différents genres 
d'obligations trouvées en structures de protéine. Ceux-ci 
sont : (a) obligations d'hydrogène, (b) obligations du 
bisulfure, (c) obligations ioniques et (d) interactions hydrophobes.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Esta ilustração mostra os tipos diferentes das 
ligações encontradas em estruturas da proteína. Estes são: 
(a) o hidrogênio ligam-se, (b) as ligações de bissulfeto, (c)
as ligações ionic e (d) as interações hydrophobic.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Questa illustrazione mostra i generi differenti di
legami trovati in strutture della proteina. Questi sono: 
(a) l'idrogeno lega, (b) i legami bisolfurico, (c) i legami 
ionici e (d) le interazioni idrofobe.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αυτή η απεικόνιση εμφανίζει διαφορετικά είδη δεσμών 
που βρίσκονται στις πρωτεϊνικές δομές. Αυτοί είναι: 
(α) δεσμοί υδρογόνου, (β) δεσμοί δισουλφιδίου, (γ) ιοντικοί
δεσμοί και (δ) υδροφοβικές αλληλεπιδράσεις.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Esta ilustración muestra las diversas clases de 
enlaces encontrados en estructuras de la proteína. Éstos son: 
(a) el hidrógeno pega, (b) los enlaces de disulfuro, (c) los 
enlaces iónicos y (d) las interacciones hidrofóbicas.</string>
          </description>
